channel.title: Contentzpk Looking for Team
channel.description:
Looking for a developmental team for a custom server with custom skills, custom npcs, custom wild even. If you've ever been on youtube looking for rsps vids you may have come across one of ours the main promo is all about partytime all the time. I'm looking for devoted staff inside and outside the game if that sounds like you visit our forums at contentzpkforum.com post a message or pm suseto or even in game. I'll be more than happy to test you and any skills you may have. Thank you for reading below is a list of what I have and what i'm looking for.
Web Developer Coder: I currently code as well Advertisement: I currently advertise as well Forums Moderator(Keeping up with the updates etc etc.) In game reliable staff that will be on not inactive.
P.S. If you are interested contact me by messaging on here or coming in game. Also looking for a coder that can code in for instance quests etc etc.
These updates are available as well
